column5: Woke up, couldn't get back to sleep, should go back to try for a few more Z's or should I just put the coffee on and keep on going?  Whatever the decision I make, have a good morning Lew and all you other early risers.
G'day Harry, nice to see you up bright & early enjoying the best part of the day
Good morning to you too! I'm on my second cup already but I might crawl back in bed and try to get another hour sleep.
Morning gents, it's a great time of the day, Pikehunter, stay up and enjoy it  Maureen
Put the pot on and am sitting here with a coffee by my side.  I'd offer you one but you know how it is, no way to get it through the internet connection.
That's ok I'm a tea tottler (sp?) in the morning anyway, but hey, thanks for the thought  Maureen
I HATE when My dad wakes up then wakes my mom and I both up. Im not saying who my father is but you all know him as the person who hunts Pike
just so everyone knows  morning starts at 5:30 am everything before that is night..so you should be saying good night not good morning.......LOL
